issue.title: Ft link admin page with api
issue.body:
#### What does this PR do?
This PR link all the admin pages to the backend API. Admin can create event, see all users, promote users to admin and other admin priviledges

#### Description of Task to be completed
- Link pages to API
- Refactor code

#### How should this be manually tested
- `git clone this branch`
- click on any admin page

#### What are the relevant stories
- Admin can perform administrative priviledges
